Name: Midnight Market
About the game: Welcome to the Midnight Market, the seedy underbelly of the city where danger lurks around every corner. In this game, you'll step into the shoes of a street-savvy hustler, buying and selling drugs to make a quick buck. But be warned - the market is cutthroat, and one wrong move can lead to a knife fight or a run-in with the law. Navigate the winding alleys and shadowy corners of the city, keeping a keen eye out for potential threats and opportunities. You'll need to outsmart rival dealers, avoid nosy cops, and dodge ruthless muggers if you want to make it to the top. With every deal you make, you'll climb the ranks of the Midnight Market, earning a reputation as a savvy and feared player. But success comes at a price, and the higher you climb, the more dangerous your enemies become. Do you have what it takes to thrive in the cutthroat world of the Midnight Market? Or will you become just another casualty of the streets? The choice is yours, but remember - in this world, there are no second chances.
